<div class="badge"><span class="badge-dot"></span>Buyer's question</div>
<h1 class="hero-h">What Is Claude Enterprise? <em style="color:#00C853;font-style:italic;">Claude for larger orgs and regulated use.</em></h1>
<p class="hero-sub">Claude Enterprise is Anthropic's top-tier plan — designed for larger organizations, regulated industries, and use cases needing the strongest data handling commitments. Here's what's in it and who should consider it.</p>
<div class="tldr"><div class="tldr-l">Short answer</div><p class="tldr-p">Claude Enterprise is Anthropic's top business tier — adds SSO/SCIM, expanded admin and audit, larger context windows, custom data retention, and signed agreements (DPA, BAA). For organizations with 150+ seats, regulated data, or compliance commitments.</p></div>
</div></div>

<div style="background:#0A1A0A;border-top:1px solid #1A3A1A;border-bottom:1px solid #1A3A1A;padding:1.25rem 2.5rem;">
<div style="max-width:880px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;font-size:0.78rem;color:#8FAF8F;">
<div>By <a href="/about" style="color:#F0FFF0;text-decoration:none;font-weight:500;">Bill Colbert</a> · <span style="color:#4A6A4A;">Founder, Treetop Growth Strategy</span></div>
<div style="color:#4A6A4A;">Published May 2026 · <a href="/content-library" style="color:#8FAF8F;text-decoration:none;">More from the library</a></div>
</div>
</div>

<section><div class="sec-inner"><h2 class="h2">What's in Enterprise that Team doesn't have</h2><ul class="ul"><li><strong>SSO with SAML / Okta / Azure AD / Google Workspace.</strong></li><li><strong>SCIM provisioning</strong> — automate user lifecycle from your IdP.</li><li><strong>Enhanced audit logging</strong> — track admin actions and usage at the audit level.</li><li><strong>Custom data retention</strong> — configure how long conversation data is retained.</li><li><strong>Signed BAA</strong> available for healthcare customers handling PHI.</li><li><strong>Signed DPA</strong> for EU customers.</li><li><strong>Higher rate limits</strong> and expanded context windows on supported models.</li><li><strong>Dedicated customer success</strong> contact at Anthropic.</li></ul></div></section>
<section><div class="sec-inner"><h2 class="h2">Who needs Enterprise</h2><ul class="ul"><li>Organizations with 150+ Claude seats.</li><li>Healthcare organizations handling PHI (require BAA).</li><li>Financial services firms with stringent compliance.</li><li>Legal firms with confidentiality requirements that need enhanced audit.</li><li>Companies with corporate SSO requirements.</li><li>EU-based or EU-serving companies needing DPA + data residency.</li><li>Public sector / government contracting where audit requirements apply.</li></ul></div></section>
<section><div class="sec-inner"><h2 class="h2">How to think about the cost</h2><p class="body">Enterprise is priced individually, not per-seat publicly. Cost scales with seats and features. Typical enterprise pricing is meaningfully higher per-seat than Team — but at scale, the security and compliance features are worth it.</p><p class="body">If you do NOT have a specific reason to need Enterprise features, Team is fine. Many organizations overspend by buying Enterprise when Team would have sufficed.</p></div></section>
<section><div class="sec-inner"><h2 class="h2">How to evaluate</h2><ol class="ol"><li>List the specific features you need (BAA? SSO? SCIM? expanded context?).</li><li>Match those to what's available in Team vs Enterprise.</li><li>If everything you need is in Team, save the money.</li><li>If you need 2+ Enterprise-only features, upgrade is justified.</li></ol></div></section>

<section><div class="sec-inner"><h2 class="h2">FAQ</h2>
<div class="faq-q"><h3 class="faq-qh">How do I get a BAA for Claude?</h3><p class="faq-qa">Through Claude Enterprise sales. BAA is not available on Team or Pro tiers.</p></div>
<div class="faq-q"><h3 class="faq-qh">Can I get Enterprise for a small team?</h3><p class="faq-qa">Sometimes — Anthropic will sometimes accommodate smaller orgs that need Enterprise features (BAA, SSO). Discuss with sales.</p></div>
<div class="faq-q"><h3 class="faq-qh">Is Enterprise required for SOC 2 compliance?</h3><p class="faq-qa">Not always. Anthropic's SOC 2 report applies across tiers. Enterprise adds features that make YOUR SOC 2 commitments easier to meet.</p></div>
<div class="faq-q"><h3 class="faq-qh">Can I switch from Team to Enterprise smoothly?</h3><p class="faq-qa">Yes. Anthropic supports the upgrade path; data and Projects move with you.</p></div>
<div class="faq-q"><h3 class="faq-qh">How does Claude Enterprise compare to ChatGPT Enterprise?</h3><p class="faq-qa">Comparable feature sets. Picking between them often comes down to other factors (writing quality, integration needs).</p></div>
</div></section>

